values:
ok, so i wake up this morning, walk downstaris, fall down the stairs, and spill my coffee all over me. then i listened to pedro the lion and sunny day realestate for about two hours and swayed. a lot. my pants finally dried.

went to cafe to get coffee (and shoprite to get sleepy things) and walked around the cemetary for a few hours which was real neat but real sad and whatever.

got home, talked to stoogie for a loooong time and cut my finger open on a ping pong ball </3. not doing so well today.

went to jenns then benitos which was crazy. mainly cause lara and jenn are crazy.

then to tuscan. the only place in warwick worth spending mass amounts of time. got my third cup of coffee. didn't spill any of it. <3. watched a few amazing bands, heard a few amazing poems, and stuff. new fave band = dylan, mike, myles, and tall dude. anyone know the name? do tell.

lara pees a lot.

stopped by adj's for a while, which was amazing casue i see her about once every six months. amy was there too. and jordan who's real neat. and the dip was wonderful <3.

boarding tomarrow with stoogie. first time going to creek with him this season?? woah. that should not be legal.

another snowday! sucks though, cause we still have no snow. whatevaaaa. not complaining. anything's better than school. so i went to law's which was neat, but i still suck at mario cart.

i broke my board </3. again. thank god i work at the board shop. i'd be broke right now if i didnt. i managed to break both rachets.

friday tomarrow <3 <3. bowling with law and claude and people. finally get to meet the dude. jess better come.

alright im out...

<3 Jul

wahoo! first snowday. that was nice. reallly didn't wanna get out of bed this morning. so i woke up around 10 and went bowling with nora lara scoot and schtoogie. it was preatty neat. i still hate bowling shoes. then we had pizza and shoprite and i hung out with schtoogie and whatnot. big d is comming back to the chance. awesome. and they're playing with gabes band, the naked citizens (www.thenakedcitizens.com). really awesome. its on a monday night. not awesome. not awesome at all. anyone know where i can get a cheep feret? <3 Jul

Alright, so <red>Anterrabae</red> is my new fave band. for the time being. i love their lyrics more that their music, but both are most excelent. 

i finally used my early leave today and went boarding. i'll probally do that every "d" day now. those are always boring in lunch anyway. yeah. back to snowboarding. it was neat. the snow sucked, but there were no lines so it was all good. and i finalyl got to check out the north park, although i didnt go in because i was broke, and apparently i need to buy a five dollar pass to use the park. whatevaaaaa. 

for all who were concerned, i've talked to tom and his sholder blade has not eaten him yet. keyword : yet. nah, but he's doing ok. he's still out for a month though. </3.

on to better news. i don't think i have any. at all. not in an emo way, just in the way that i've got absolutely nothing else good to report.

on that note, so long and thanks for all the shoes.

<3 Jul

<redtext>Heyy. I haven't updated this thing in forever. I completely forgot about it untill I was Bobby's yesterday. So how's it going? I don't think anything important has happened since June. Well a few things. Summer started. Got a job. Worked a lot. The Dispatch broke up </3. I went to camp. Got another job. School started. One job ended, quit the other one. Went to Mass. Saw a bunch of shows. Got second job back. Creek opened. Winter break. Went to New Hampshire. School started again. That's all. Yeah....

Anyway. I think I'll start updating this thingy more often. But its winter, and snowboarding is taking up my life. I get out of school at 12 tomarrow to go to the mountain. Wahoo!

<3 Jul </redtext>

hey guys. i really don't wanna go back to school. yeah... only three more days of work. hmm... its sad, but ill miss work more than id ever miss school. who knows. maybe i was just cut out to serve ice cream. lets hope not. rick brought me a toaster strudal this morning. he's awesome. wahoo back to school shopping tomarrow. at the thrift shop. about time i get myself some new clothing. well... you know what i mean. i need a skirt. wow this is the most pointlessly boring making no sense in no logical order post ever. i think ill just get more coffee and leave you know... goodbye...

wahoo! nora fixed my livejournal. i killed it. a lot. just ask her. it was pretty bad. so now its nifty. there are a few things i might change but other than that its rad. so i guess ill start writing in it again. especially becaue school it almost here </3 </3. i don't wanan go! at all. meh. yeah. summer was neat. over too soon. i gotta go. scotts suposta be picking me up at the moment. going to see without a paddle. it looks hilarious. yeah. im gonna meat him at the end of my block. later.
hey look at this possible new layout like it?? remember though...

DAMN IT

i will figure this out
alright. this is the first attempt to put pictures on this thing. this is a random picture. dotn mind it.

hello again. tonight was great. i get home from school "jul did you talk to scott today?" "erm yeah why?" "about what?" "erm i forget why" "was it about the fact that were going to his house tonight?" "what no... we are?" yeah. so i go to scotts. and get greated by three kids and water guns. scott and two three years old recruits. I'm wet. very wet. and i wore a white shirt. smart of me... but thankfully i borrowed a black one. hehe ph34r. yeah.... but the shirts huge on me so ill give it back </3. anyyyway. so they spent wayyyy too much time trying to get me into the pool. then i stole scotts cds and he couldnt get them or throw me in the pool with them so i was safe. my the way im thinking of getting a ligit blog a la tripod. back to scotts. they decided to drench me anyway. with every form of water they could find. but they did not get me into the pool! well sorta. i half went in the hot tub later. but that was different and volentary. so (by the way this entary is in no logical order.) i was running down the road (or couple roads) with no shoes on being chassed by a boy with a large bucket of water. then i steped on a large rock with my heel. its swolen and bruised and i dont think ill be able to walk toamorw. and jon like killed himself by running next to the pool, falling, and quite possably smashing a calcium deposite and cutting up his leg prtty bad. he wasammusing watching him walk up and down the staris after that. he looked sco'ish. the country, not the boy. i know for a fact im forgeting main hilarious things that heppened. jonscoot... hit up the comment button. speaking of coments lara where are you? im not feeling creative today. sorry for not exactly doing this justice. oh oh oh and bonnie is getting a mega hot car over the weekend. and there was this knife... you should have seen it. it had three knifes that poped out of the sides. and it looked like a chineese star only wit three points and knives on each end. and it folded into a cute little circle. <3. and mario donkey kong?? what?? i think thats awesome. turing out to be a pretty good week in terms of surprises. like the fact that no one told me screaching weasel got back together <3 <3. that was the best news ever. i really wanna go to one of their shows. hmm i think im gonna go write to scotts dads boss. in order to get him off from work. so he can take us to the show. woot. catch 22, big d and the kids table, reel big fish, rx bandits, and lucky boys confussion. moi, jon, scott, et nora. this shall be amazing. i cant wait. but i gotta see if scotts dad got off of work. :::the suspense::: but it hink he might have. i think he should just call in sick anyway. whatevaaa. ok im out. i got a stomach ache. and i wanna talk to val...

<3 Jul

hey guys! well... i shall write about yesterday. friday. fridays are always good. especially when they involve pimp hats and teacups. so i get home and realise noones gonig to rockapalosa. including me. long story there. so i get on my bike and meet jon at the triangle. apparently people with cars dont like me. between the guy who gave me the finger and chris yelling something alog the lines of "your fucking queer" out of the window of his tic tac, i came to this conclusion. so we get to the triangle and jon brought the map we needed to bury. once i figure out how to upload pics with html ill put it here. if you know please tell me. sooooo then we realise that neither of ys were smart enough to bring a shovel. large sticks and peices of slate work. right? so out hole was just big enough to slide our map in its duct tape case into. then we cover it in peables. and rocks. and bigger rocks. and a frickin bolder to top it off. so then we get back on out bikes and go to jons house for a while. and his brothers were eating the worlds best cerial. whats the name? so then we watched vidios including arts of hte stoned cam i havent seen in 98434058305830485 years. then scott picks us up and were off to the bazzarr. and we're early. so they decide to steal my bag and climb a very big tree with it. i got it back. so we see a sign and cant think of anything to rearange the letters into quick enough so we leave the sign. later someone wrote nude bar. next was 63 tits. finially it opens. so we go on a few rides, but some funnel cake. we went of the teacups. and jons strong. and we flew. and all got really dizzy and got really bad headaches. and then got off and found out what it was like to be high. only with much more headaches. then we hit up the booths. and i got a pimp hat!!! and it was grande. and large and green. its awesome. im never gonna take it off. and we really wanted this carnies hat and after rounds of water guns he decided to give us the hat as a prize. scott got it. so me and scott were pimps. by the way to you guys... i got my wallet back! with the money intact! today sucked ass. tomaorw will two. i hate family. <3 Jul

heyy! so i supose i should put the events of the last day and a half in order. how about that? Ok. so. last night i went to dyls and that was neat. even though i didnt brign a bathingsuit and had to borrow one and yeah. so we swam and ate and talked. a lot. and amde a fire. or at least attempted to. it was a pathetic fire. but apparently a hot pathetic fire. Peirce and Julian and me and Dyl were there. and of corse we come up with the great idea of burning duct tape. it looks neat and it drips little duct tape drips. but they're really hot. and i was burning a strand and it burnt really close to my hand so i went to let it go and realsied it was stuck to my finger and i burnt my finger and now its swolen and a odd shade of green-gray-red-purple. sorta nasty but its pretty around the outsides. then i went home and found my earings <3 i was so happy becasue i lost them. and then they came back. and it was grand.

so then today i wake up and go to town because i promased the bandies id go to the parade. so i went and read for a while and then peirce scared the living crap out of me. so i hung out with him and janson for a while untill the parade came which was at 11 even though it said it would start at 10 and id been there since 9 45. fun. so we watch it and they leave. and i ride around town for a really long time then go back and read. then go to cafe a la mode to get a mochachino shake. even though its really cold. so i go to kara house to get pants becasue im doing this all in boxers and its not warm. then we hang out for a little while and i go ride for quite a bit more and fianlly chase the parade and catch up with them at memorial at which time a man speaks and some guys shoot guns and some pimps take out swords and it was classic. so then i hug Dyl talk to jess for a while and ride home.

Then scott tells me about this amazing show with catch and big d neer his dads work and we wanna go so bad and yeah. it shall be grand.

Now im off to nonnies with lisa and kara.

<3 Jul

hey guys... Phish broke up </3 </3. First time I ever heard of phish was at camp with Adrienne and Zack. Poster is dead - hit by a commet. thats not the name of the "song" or aything. that is harpona. you might wanna check the spelling of that. anyway. it was very upsetting. because we had been thinking avbout them a lot the past two days and didnt know why. then we found out they broke up. May 25th 2004. yes, the summer tour is still on. i dunno how many people asked me that.dyls going to a show. i really want to. dyl's gonna see if her sister will take us to their last show. that would be spectacular. yes.

off subject. its memorial weekend suckaaa! mhmm. last night i went and saw shrek two with law and jess. me and jess were gonna walk home from school but the weather killed that plan. so we got a ride. then proceded to walk to pennings. awesome day. shrek was good. i dunno if it was as good as the first one. jess and law were convinsed it was bettter. i think rach was right though. shrek on crack. and apparently the person sitting behin law was gonna kill her. so we had to sprint out of the thearter..... but i got a phish and pennywise cd at the mall. along with multitudes of candy.

today! i woke up and went to a yardsale in pine. where i saw jons neighbor and was thoraly confused for who knows how long. mr. micferson. i like him though. so then i went to the country dream for pancakes. went home showered went to town with kara. we ate and chilled and drove! kara got her permit and can now drive us around. shes a good driver. well... yes. good driver. not good parker. or turnner into roader. but its all good. i love her anyway <3. Then i went out for ANOTHER meal and almost exploded. but im ok. so i came home and changed my livejournal format yet again. i like this one. i tink ill keep it for a while. but the way it says "in that moment" on the bottom.

ok well ill leave you now. and put this link back in my info. lattttterrrrrr

<3 Jul

hey. my head hurts. yep. so erm today was decent. wont bore you with details of the day. half because i dont remember any of it. all i remember is talking to alex dutring english and how hilarious nolan and callora are in math. mhmmm. and i watched king kong. the origonal one. its amusing. who knows why my dad loves it.. yeah so then i went to the pond/clearing/forest/whateverthehellyouwannacallit. that was great as always. i love that place. well thats all for now. im contimplating getting advil.

ok so this is the part where i dont even try to make an excuse for where ive been the past few weeks. i supose my life was eventful. im not even gonna go into that. and at the moment im painting my nails with elmers glue because my nail polish isnt white enough. wow.... i didnt say that. elmers glue dries clear. wow. im home alone for a few hours. woot. and damn todays only monday. why dont i have white nail polish? yeah. today was the last meet. its sad. and im still trying to figure out how to put pictures in this. i think photobucket might try to help. but im not sure. im chnaging my background again. that shall be fun. so i supose ill write about my weekend. friday i went to conneticut and i dont have pt anymore! i love this. so saturday i get up then soon after i go to west point with darceys, "w", shaun and some guy that looks like bob the builder? and val. it was neat. even though id rather have stayed home and gone out with kev jess key and johnny but its all good. so we had water gun fights in the back of the pizza restruant with water guns which we previouusly bought at the dollar store next door. and ate collectively 36 slices of pizza. they must deserve aome kind of award for that. it was insanity to watch. those boys are hilarious. and football game? what football game?? yeah what? oh we watched it... when people stood up and cheared... so we were playing egyption... and val bit my arm off... thats the bloody stump on the end of my sholder. mhmmm... so yeah. then sunday i get up ride to town then go to jesses. and have a burning party with johnnys cds. yeah. so i think ill go now and change the background, upload formal pics, and get an oreo. <3 Jul

ok so rach is right. most of my bands sing about smoking cigs. which i was thinking alot about last night. cigs, not music. well that too. anyway. they should be legal and good for you. i was also contiplating everything contemplatable. and got no sleep.

i need to get out of here. id do anything. i wanna start over. just leave. yuo dont understand how wonderful that would be.

im going to write. becase u i cant think of anything more exciting to do.

ok soo last night.... i slept over karas. it was wonderful. i love her.

ill finsh later

<3 Jul

hey. its easter. so i get to clean for a few MORE hours and thten go have 20 people none of which are under 21 come over and eat dinner. def my idea of a holiday well spent </3. shoot that mean i need to dress up right?? and i dont know if i have any clean skirts! eeek!

drive in is officially open <3! lets go this year? especially if we fid someone with a car... can you walk in at the drive in? or bike in? hmmm.... ::pondering::.

last night movies with law and jess. scooooby dooby doo! yey! I love scooby <3. so does law.. and she sang the scooby doo song for maybe an hour total yesterday. it was rawking... billy idol style...

ohhh and i got a sex pistols cd. 6.99!! mhmmmm. i need to go to the thrift shop again soon. i have no clothing </3. and i need old nifty skirts. yep.. ok ill go now.

<3 Jul

hey. happy bday mrs fuca! yeha. last night was mrs. fucas bday and we went for dinner in the city. it was the best manacotti ive ever eaten. yeah. no ones around. im bored. i wanna get out of my house. but ive got no where to go! and val wont answer her phone and laws still at tap. toamotws easter. a bunch of fam comming over. yeah. wow im boring today...

<3 Jul

hey guys. short entry tonight. im sitting on a chair arm and my rear end hurts. anyyyway. vegas last week. it was awesome. when i get pictures ill try to load them and hope im not too retarded. which i easly could be. but yeah. nothing really to say on that front. i got home and ate an orange and went to the track with jesse. i think im hopeless </3. i forgot to jump. and ran a hurdle down.... yeah... then i went back to his house which worked out much better. nothing to jump over. yeah. ok il go now. i want friends.... real, animate ones. couches dont count. nor do guitars, leather jackets, stereos, or stuffed dogs named <inserts dogs name here>

haha today was well.... interesting. it was april fools day. which resulted in extra 400s, scott getting really pissed, and the rest of us cracking up at random times. jokes of the day --- well first abbate asked kay to formal... johnna tried to kiss kay... kay jumped 0943850398 ft backwords.... track team hid on coach.... track team put megaphone on seiran and hid it in the trash.... scotts locker got superglued shut.... nora pretended to make out with guss -- scott wasnt too happy cant say i blame him. large amounts of other stuff that i cant remember. yeah. so er... global picked research  paper unfairly -- almost murdered foss... english had test... french partay tomarow!!! got skirt... art talked with alex and made mano wanna kill hisself. my making him play emocore. hardcore emocore. yeah.... lunch plotted scotts demise probally talked about something sexually relatedcant remember. still havent seen this ben kid.... bio watched platapus movie. chimps tomaorw! i better move my seat... math filled out politocal survey about flag burining and musicians rights. calora is a 97 year old non us citizen with a 4.0 gpa who gets mostly f's. if you see how it figures let me know... study hall slept talked about world demise and aisians... after school hung out played practical jokes on eachother meet was cancled! got pissed i still had to go to practice.. went to practice anway.... ran ladders practiced hurdles danced. had to sprint an extra 400 becsaeu we put the megaphone in the trash can on siren mode. and hid from coach. n the woods... yeah... played guitar... lazy summery of today...

yes i do. anyway. tooooooooday.... woke up dad was nice enough do drive me to school went yeah the day was nothing special. jenn cut my hair after school. i love her soo much. i also got my movielife sweatshirt. another reason i love jenn. apparently i was emo today. even more emo than im usually emo??? im emo??? who knows. tom thinks im emo. it works. so after school and after getting my hair cut i had a track meet. that was interesting. good i guess. i have no idea what sprinters are suposed to get. i did hurdles. i like them. a lot. but i still need go get my speed down and crap. so uh ive got nothing to write about. so ill talk about something random. like dylans skirt. i swear. im in love. this thing is awesome. i love all dylans skirts. but this one especially. it was so neat. mag gave it to her becasue she didnt like it. how could you not? it was really long and twirly and yeah. nifty i tell you. so i decided i need to wear more skirts. accually i decided that yesterday is french with rach;s amazing skirt. that was neat too. it was long and neat and red and yeah. but it was sorta orange? ill see if my mother has any neat ones and if not ill make a few as soon as i get to middle town. alright im gongi skirt hunting in my house. aka my moms old stuff from when she was little and forgot she had.

<3 Jul

friday
track meet. woot! it as great. i got there and my event was like there so i go and do hurdles. and i didnt fall. so i was happy. even though i didnt exactially win i didny die. so its all good. then i put my warm up stuff on just in time to take it off and run a 400. that was interesting. i didnt fall into the middle of the track which was my only fear. so it was all good. adn then same deal with warm ups. i go tripple jump. fouled every single time! i didnt know tht was possable. believe me its not that hard. then i was done. so i go see tom and we go down the street to the deli. and get sexually stimulating gummy peaches. they were fun. then we go back to the armory and tom is told hes the greatest living person by this homeless guy. oh and tom gave me his jacket. so hes the best ever. so we go watch a few events i find jesse and we hang out and watch peopel run and the biff chant made biff "mad quick". he won by like a frickin mile on the 400? i tihnk 4. it was insane. and all cuza the biff chant. and everyone did good. yeah. then on the bus home we talked. a lot. i cant remeber anytihing else from it though. the ride there i freeked everyone out my accident. sorry girls.

saturday
i wokw up and made a few calls and landed at jesses house. with my guitar. and toms jacket. with every intention of giving it back that night. sorta. so we played and yeah. im still not a good trumpeter. then jon left and a few min later so did to. we went over to pats. that was fun. i love pats house and his mothers cooking. and we roasted marshmellows aka had a burning marshmellow and stick fight. that was awesome. and we played a bunch of pool. im getting better. when we dont play by cami rules. then i got dropped off by tom. i still have his jacket.

today
i got up and went shopping. and got my formal dress. its awesome. its ywllow. wih black bows. which sounds like an ugly bee. but its really neat. pretty julia too. thats what i was gonig for. its nifty. and i relised i hate most stuff sold at mallls. saves the food. and hot topic. and that awesome 283 jacket. i wanted it so badley. it was awesome. but ill make one just at nifty. then i got home and went to jesses. i love him. that was fun. adn we listened to the beastie boys. there awesome. i tihnk ill go now....

<3 Jul

ok uppppppppppdate time. yes, update can only be spelt with 10 p's. except where i just wrote it. but we can pretend?? so track meet toamtrw in new york. woot? i think so. even though none of you girls are going? yeah. i cant wait. 400 open 55 hurdles and tripple jump. still not quite sure how those are gonna work out but well manage. somehow. ok talking in third person again. gotta stop that. apparently im scaring scott. speaking of scott nora was gonna lik him today? yeah. who knows. weird people i tell you. so today. it was alright. global decent. english was horable because my besst friend jenn wasnt there. not cool. french test. not good. even rach was having trouble. that takes a pretty hard test. i want eggs. art was neat. listened to ska, drew my log cabin which isnt comming out all that bad. its pretty neat. lunch we had a balogna fight. it was scarry. especially since im scared of balogna. i think it all started when amy chassed my down the road with a piece in fourth grade. she usta put it in her mac and cheese. i think ill have mac and cheese with my turky club tonight. no jesse, i didnt not join a turkey club. im hungry if you cant tell. really hungry. and dinner is taking its time. right next period. wow. biology. reproduction. sitting in front of kay. bad idea. and did you know snakes have two penis? me either. i didnt think i needed to know that. your hair grows 6 inces per year. so then was math. got tests back. not cool. 85 or 90. still not sure which. regardless nolan beat me.. i saw his sister a few days ago. when i was wearing my striped coler shirt with the blue bar shirt over it and plad pants. she was pretty amazed i was running in stripes and plaids? yep. then lab. we were all yelling at eachother and knife useage and who had to look at the microscope and how to do the lab any everything else arguable. i mean everything. then we went to the vending machines. ohhh today the punk ramp was taken over by the ghetto people. it was pretty intimidating and there were 9564383860456 ghetto people! exactally. i counted. they were scarry. poor punks. so the ghetto people have there ramp. the punks have their ramp. the trackies have there vending machines. figures. were all pigs. kay got thrown into a vending machine by chris yesterday and has shown my the bruise at least 20 times. in two days. then track i ran. by myself. becase my running buddies werent there/dropped the workout. so i finished quickly and hurdled for a half hour. im getting better. i swear. i really am. sorta. i can do the little touch foot thing with other hand thingy. good thing becase this time tomarow ill be doing it. in the armory. mhmmm. it smells like bacon!!!! i think dinners ready!!!! im out.

<3 Jul

never thought this would happen eh? jul accually updating live journal?? wattttttttt? and i dont agree with many of the things listed below as lifes greatest feelings. but thats just me. some of them are good.i thihkn snowboarding in a tshirt should also be added. becase that is one of the great feelings in life. but anyway. you may be wondering why i havent updated in forever? wellt he answer is... im lazy. im a bum. that is the sole reason. not becase i didnt have time. i had time.yeah. so whats happened lately? nothing. not that i can think of track started. thts neat. i love it. and ive got a meat?? on friday?? and coach put me in tripple jump and high hurdles??? who knows. ill write more lader.

ok. all three of those days were awesome. friday i get home from school and go to jesses house for a few hours before the dance. his dad has the absolute best drum set ever. then we played with jackie and jill who happen to be the best dogs ever. notice a patern? yes, jesse is the best guy ever as well. so then we hung out and had dinner which was great. i love mrs.fucas cooking. especially fried chicken. its the best ever? haha. then we went to the dance. which could have been better. i mean it was fun but yeah. jesse tried to go in with a wolverine mask and hood but he wasnt alowed in. for some reason im happy about thaT? so yeah went home wasnt my best night for sleeing but i managed. then sat i woke up and cant remember for the life of me what i did. did rick come over? maybe? who knows. then i went to jons at 6 and that was fun. there were about 9543860938540395 million people and yeah. so we hung out listened to music fought with val and ended up killing my hands, made plans to capture jons couch. then we played manhunt wich as always ended pretty badly. then we went inside and danced with his slightly drunk parents and made a congo line which ended in a huge pile up. but it was fun. i think nora got it on camra. then val slept over and theres fucking gohsts in my atic. literally. that was great. so we stayed up for a while talking about the most ranodm things on the face of the earth. so she left pretty early the next morning then jess and jonscoot came over.
